<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> ( <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">2.09</measure>   × <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.84</measure>   × <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.84</measure>) with columnar <rs type="decoration">arcade</rs> design. A full length male <rs type="decoration">portrait</rs> in the centre, within an arch, is is flanked by two <rs type="decoration">figure</rs>s on either side. Those on the extreme right and the second from left hold <rs type="decoration">mask</rs>s; the second from the right holds a <rs type="decoration">lyre</rs>; that on the extrme right apparently also holds <rs type="decoration">palms</rs>. The columns between the figures uphold a <rs type="objectType">cornice</rs>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the cornice (l. 1) and on the lower moulding (l. 2). The text must have begun on the lid.</p>
</div>
